8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Elai and Rephrase.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Video, Avatar Talking Head, Templates, Voice Over. Where Elai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Auto Captions and Stock Footage, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Rephrase.ai uniquely offers Batch Processing, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Elai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Rephrase.ai scores 7/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Rephrase.ai comes in at a lower starting price of Contact sales, while Elai begins at $23/mo. Elai has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Rephrase.ai does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
