c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Elai is best suited for marketing teams, training video creation, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Rephrase.ai, meanwhile, shines for personalized marketing videos, sales outreach at scale, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2021, Elai describes itself as \"Create AI videos from text with digital avatars.\" Rephrase.ai, established in 2019, positions itself as \"Create personalized AI videos at scale.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Rephrase.ai** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0). However, this does not mean Elai is a poor choice — far from it. Elai excels in its own right, particularly for marketing teams and training video creation.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value excellent personalization api, go with Rephrase.ai. If clone your own avatar matters more to you, Elai is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
